00:22:40.440 --> 00:22:42.050 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that
the deeper you go,

00:22:42.050 --> 00:22:44.530 align:middle line:84%
you know, time itself-- Einstein
said that time is an illusion

00:22:44.530 --> 00:22:47.760 align:middle line:90%
