00:22:47.760 --> 00:22:51.070 align:middle line:84%
The shallower you're thinking,
the more quickly time moves.

00:22:51.070 --> 00:22:53.140 align:middle line:84%
The deeper you're
thinking, the more

00:22:53.140 --> 00:22:55.800 align:middle line:84%
you can expand time and through
prayer, through meditation,

00:22:55.800 --> 00:22:57.740 align:middle line:84%
through spiritual
practice, through deeper

00:22:57.740 --> 00:23:01.060 align:middle line:84%
reflection and mindfulness,
deeper conversation.

00:23:01.060 --> 00:23:02.720 align:middle line:84%
And that's really the
buzz of this moment,

00:23:02.720 --> 00:23:04.620 align:middle line:84%
and that's what we're
all moving into.

00:23:04.620 --> 00:23:06.880 align:middle line:84%
